{"tid":2510141,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［中文文學］其實個撚字都幾屈機","createTime":"2021-04-30T02:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T02:53:57.000Z","uid":343551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"01166cf7c5bcc3b193b1d007f6541cfb8fa17f09","tid":2510141,"uid":343551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"成日聽人講乜撚野 點撚樣<br />\n諗深一層個撚字真係萬能key黎<br />\n<br />\n平時我地可以當佢係名詞：條<span class=\"red\">撚</span><br />\n<br />\n想講野果陣加重個語氣 我地成日聽到既好<span class=\"red\">撚</span>熱呀 好<span class=\"red\">撚</span>正呀<br />\n<br />\n又或者係動詞 你依家<span class=\"red\">撚</span>狗呀<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">當然亦都有唔係粗口既用法呀</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如去大排檔食野會叫<span class=\"red\">撚手小菜 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚至攞黎做廣告既口號 神者<span class=\"red\">撚</span> <span class=\"red\">撚</span>太<span class=\"red\">撚</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmamp1Uczf4pnsb7rhsFkRey4dqGgnbySjXAqgnBWfXrBt?filename=TZMB3co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZMB3co.jpg&h=97c58174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rh5gmriRVXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRh5gmriRVXE&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=633f4fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rh5gmriRVXE</a>"},{"pid":"43fc3cf9112ed29534046c381dabcb130354b853","tid":2510141,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:53:57.000Z","msg":"最屈機係可以形容樓主嘅外貌-撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}